data.description: Wonderful spacious home features 2 living areas, a nice kitchen with eating area, corner stone fireplace, and a sunroom with lots of windows ideal for entertaining.  The home has been well maintained and is in the heart of town with a nice fenced in backyard.  This charming home has much to offer.
